<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="id8eb34cb7-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1959 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/86/296/s1">Pub. L. 86–296, § 1</ref>, <date date="1959-09-21">Sept. 21, 1959</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/73/572">73 Stat. 572</ref>, provided that the amendment made by that section is effective for fiscal years ending after <date date="1960-06-30">June 30, 1960</date>.</p>
