<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="miscellaneous" id="id8eb34cb8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Additional Appropriation for the Fiscal Year Ending <date date="1970-06-30">June 30, 1970</date></heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/90/574/tV/s505">Pub. L. 90–574, title V, § 505</ref>, <date date="1968-10-15">Oct. 15, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1013">82 Stat. 1013</ref>, provided that the annual appropriation for the maintenance and operation of the Gorgas Memorial Laboratory for the fiscal year ending <date date="1970-06-30">June 30, 1970</date> would be increased by $500,000.</p>
</note>
